output.sentences: Her first art project focused on and eccentric and chaotic pattern.
The next project kept the complexity, but was constructed in a more orderly fashion.
Afterwards, she went for a more natural, flowery look.
She then mixed this flowery aesthetic with the complex pattern she had learned from before.
She continued to create new pieces, using the skills and patterns the had learned from all her old projects.
